Subject:    <a href="?t=95837891200001&r=1&w=2">MX to an IP address possible?</a>
From:       <a href="?a=95837786200035&r=1&w=2">unmvax!deimos.cis.ksu.edu!cveg!cseg!dws () ucbvax ! Berkeley ! EDU  (David W !  Summers)</a>
